Package com.sun.xml.ws.config.metro.parser.jsr109

Class HandlerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.xml.ws.config.metro.parser.jsr109.HandlerType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Locatable
    public class HandlerType
extends Object
implements Locatable
    Declares the handler for a port-component, service-ref. Handlers can access the init-param name/value pairs using the HandlerInfo interface. Used in: port-component, service-ref

    Java class for handlerType complex type.
